description:
Welcome to a tour to one of the most beautiful tropical island groups in the world: the Tobago Keys. A collection of uninhabited islands that are part of Saint Vincent and the Grenadines in the Caribbean. It is a remote location, and not all that easy to get to. But definitely worth the effort, as you will hopefully come to agree during this tour. So let’s get started, shall we?

Click the *Join* button now to become a VR Gorilla YouTube member, unlocking access to the full video and our complete collection of full-length videos. https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6AXBF-78lNa3_TjAIWZWmQ/join
